OL,7,Fsince Holyrood's Standards, Procedures
OL,8,Fand Public Appointments Committee
OL,9,Fpublished its verdict against him,
OL,10,Fwhich also included a recommendation
OL,11,Fto strip him of his salary for 54 days.
