OL,6,FAnnouncing separately that he would
OL,7,Fcover the costs himself, Mr Matheson
OL,8,Frevealed the bill had been the result
OL,9,Fof his children using the device as a
OL,10,FWiFi hotspot to watch football during
OL,11,Fa holiday in Morocco.
OL,13,FThe former minister initially denied
OL,14,Fthere had been any inappropriate use
OL,15,Fof the device, when asked by
OL,16,Fjournalists. After months of pressure
OL,17,Fon him, Mr Matheson stood down as
OL,18,Fhealth secretary in February.
