OL,6,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,7,Fsaid the comments from the First
OL,8,FMinister were "utterly unbelievable
OL,9,Fand embarrassing".
OL,11,FHe added: "He has demeaned himself and
OL,12,Fthe office of First Minister. Two
OL,13,Fweeks in and the pretence of a new
OL,14,Fkind of Government is gone. Party
OL,15,Ffirst ` country second."
OL,17,FUrging the First Minister to "do the
OL,18,Fright thing for once", he called on Mr
OL,19,FSwinney to demand Mr Matheson's
OL,20,Fresignation.
